msgstr ""
"Prosesnya dimulai saat kandidat mengisi formulir. Setiap pemohon secara "
"otomatis diberi Nomor Pendaftaran unik (misalnya PMB/2026/0001)."

#. module: campus_pmb
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_pmb.pmb_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"The system restricts PMB Committee access rights. Committee members can only"
" view and process candidates who apply to the Faculty or Study Program under"
" their responsibility. Candidate privacy is guaranteed."
msgstr ""
"Sistem membatasi hak akses Komite PMB. Anggota panitia hanya dapat melihat "
"dan memproses calon yang melamar ke Fakultas atau Program Studi yang berada "
"di bawah tanggung jawabnya. Privasi kandidat terjamin."

#. module: campus_pmb
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_pmb.pmb_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"The system will block acceptance if the required documents are incomplete or"
" payment proof is unverified. Transitions between states are tightly "
"controlled by backend algorithms."
msgstr ""
"Sistem akan memblokir penerimaan jika dokumen yang diperlukan tidak lengkap "
"atau bukti pembayaran tidak terverifikasi. Transisi antar negara dikontrol "
"secara ketat oleh algoritma backend."

